<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Ahaṁ bhante, tisaraṇena saha, aṭṭhaṅga-samannāgataṁ uposatha-sīlaṁ, dhammaṁ yācāmi, anuggahaṁ katvā sīlaṁ detha, me bhante.</span></p>
