</ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 27pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">我受持離高、大床座學處。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p>
