<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">尊者大德我（向您）求授三皈與五戒， 請慈悲地滿足我的請求。</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p>
