<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Buddhaṁ saranaṁ gacchāmi.</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Dhammaṁ saranaṁ gacchāmi.</span></p>
