<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">第二次我皈依佛，</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">第二次我皈依法，</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:18pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt">第二次我皈依僧；</span></p>
