<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Idaṁ me sīlaṁ magga-phala nānassa paccayo hotu</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:mingliu; font-size:12pt">願我此功德，為證道果緣</span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Imaṁ no punna-bhāgaṁ sabbasattānaṁ dema.</span></p>
