<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Microsoft Yahei'; font-size:12pt"> </span></p>
<p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 18pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Sabbe sattā sukhitā hontu.</span></p>
