<p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:45pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Arial Unicode MS'; font-size:12pt">　　「不，大德！」</span></p>
<ol start="8" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1"><li style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; line-height:130%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt 33.18pt; padding-left:2.82pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Sannā niccā vā aniccā vā'ti. Aniccā Bhante. Yaṁ panāniccaṁ, dukkhaṁ vā taṁ sukhaṁ vāti. Dukkhaṁ Bhante. Yaṁ panāniccaṁ dukkhaṁ vipari-ṇāma dhammaṁ kallaṁ nu taṁ samanupassituṁ etaṁ mama esohamasmi eso me attāti. No hetaṁ Bhante.</span></li>
