<p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Arial Unicode MS'; font-size:12pt">「而凡為無常的、苦的、變易法，你們適合認為：『這是我的，我是這個，這是我的真我』嗎？」</span></p>
<p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:120%; margin:0pt 0pt 6pt 36pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:36pt"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Arial Unicode MS'; font-size:12pt">　　「不，大德！」</span></p>
<ol start="9" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt" type="1"><li style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; line-height:130%; margin:0pt 0pt 8pt 33.18pt; padding-left:2.82pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt; vertical-align:baseline"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:Tahoma; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic; font-weight:bold; vertical-align:baseline">Saṅkhārā niccā vā aniccā vāt'i. Aniccā bhante. Yaṁ panāniccaṁ dukkhaṁ vā taṁ sukhaṁ vāti. Dukkhaṁ bhante. Yaṁ panāniccaṁ dukkhaṁ vipari-ṇāma dhammaṁ kallaṁ nu taṁ samanupassituṁ etaṁ mama esohamasmi eso me attāti. No hetaṁ bhante.</span></li>
